## File Upload

- Chunk size: **50MB**
- Token refresh before each chunk for long uploads
- Use AbortController for cancellation

---

## Real-time Subscriptions

```typescript
useEffect(() => {
	const channel = supabase
		.channel("dataset_changes")
		.on("postgres_changes", {
			event: "UPDATE",
			schema: "public",
			table: "v2_statuses",
		}, async (payload) => {
			// Validate ownership before invalidating
			const { data } = await supabase
				.from("v2_datasets")
				.select("user_id")
				.eq("id", payload.new.dataset_id)
				.single();

			if (data?.user_id !== userId) return;
			queryClient.invalidateQueries(["userDatasets", userId]);
		})
		.subscribe();

	return () => supabase.removeChannel(channel);
}, [userId]);
```

